<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hide-v">hide <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /haɪd/    美 /haɪd/  </p>
<p>(hid, hidden)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(把…) 藏起来；隐藏：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She and her family hid away for nearly twenty-five months before they were discovered. 
她和家人躲藏了近25个月后才被发现。</p><footer>人教① – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>遮掩；遮挡：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sunglasses make someone appear mysterious, because they hide the eyes.  
墨镜让人看上去很神秘，因为它们遮住了眼睛。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>隐瞒；掩饰：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a hidden meaning
隐含的意义</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>hid</strong> the sad news <strong>from</strong> their son.
他们对儿子隐瞒了这个伤心的消息。</p></div></div>